source:
TEXT_BANPIX125_03713_SEQ_00Uin Nee appears even more restless than usual, which should be cause for no small amount of alarm.

※Please note that the difficulty of this quest has been synced to your current level. Furthermore, you may not proceed with a class or job that is different from when you accepted this quest.
target:
TEXT_BANPIX125_03713_SEQ_00Règle spéciale:  synchronisation de quête avec limitation de job ou de classe
Il n'est possible de progresser dans cette quête qu'avec la classe ou le job qui a servi à la commencer.

Uin Nee semble très agitée.

source: TEXT_BANPIX125_03713_TODO_00<tab>Defeat the Nu Mou porxienappers in Sextuplet Shallow.
target: TEXT_BANPIX125_03713_TODO_00<tab>Vaincre <var 33 ((BNpcName)) 02F223D50302 /var> près du bas-fond des Sextuplés
TEXT_BANPIX125_03713_TODO_02<tab>Parler à Uin Nee, à Lydha Lran

source: TEXT_BANPIX125_03713_UINNEE_000_000<tab>Well, favorite mortal, we <var 1A 02 /var>could<var 1A 01 /var> be frolicking with porxies in dreams right now. But nooo! Those awful, nasty lawless ones just had to go and make off with the one I ordered from Pla Enni, so both I <var 1A 02 /var>and<var 1A 01 /var> the dreams are...porxieless!
target: TEXT_BANPIX125_03713_UINNEE_000_000<tab><var 2C ((<var 29 EB02 /var>)) (( )) 02 /var>, c'est horrible<var 1D /var>! J'avais commandé un porxie à Pla Enni mais ces vilains Nu Mousard l'ont capturé<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_BANPIX125_03713_UINNEE_000_001<tab>Ugh! Ugh, I say! Oooh, when I get my hands on those porxienappers...
target: TEXT_BANPIX125_03713_UINNEE_000_001<tab>Sans sa jolie truffe ailée, je pourrai pas emmener mes trouvailles dans le monde des rêves...

source: TEXT_BANPIX125_03713_UINNEE_000_002<tab>Wait! I don't need to get my hands on them! Because we have your much larger hands! Good, good. Go and punch a porxienapper in the face for me, mortal!
target: TEXT_BANPIX125_03713_UINNEE_000_002<tab>Je t'en prie, va le retrouver pour moi<var 1D /var>! Il a disparu dans les alentours du bas-fond des Sextuplés.

source: TEXT_BANPIX125_03713_SYSTEM_000_005<tab>The porxie is considerably calmed by your ministrations. After sparing you an affectionate snort, it turns toward Lydha Lran.
target: TEXT_BANPIX125_03713_SYSTEM_000_005<tab>Le porxie est très heureux de vous voir et vous témoigne de sa gratitude avant de repartir vers Lydha Lran.

source: TEXT_BANPIX125_03713_UINNEE_000_010<tab>Safe and sound! And round! And cute! Exactly what I was hoping for! I can spin the loveliest of dreams with a porxie so charming...
target: TEXT_BANPIX125_03713_UINNEE_000_010<tab>Te revoilà<var 1D /var>! Le porxie est aussi arrivé à bon port, et sans une égratignure<var 1D /var>! Heu<var 16 /var>reu<var 16 /var>se<var 16 /var>ment que tu étais là pour donner une leçon à ces vilains Nu Mousard<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_BANPIX125_03713_UINNEE_000_011<tab><sigh> But first I suppose I should inform the Nu Mou in Pla Enni that it arrived safely after all. They were so very <var 1A 02 /var>anxious<var 1A 01 /var> about it. Some fae really need to learn to calm down, if you ask me...
target: TEXT_BANPIX125_03713_UINNEE_000_011<tab>Je m'occupe de rassurer les Nu Mou de Pla Enni, tu sais comment ils sont<var 1D /var>! Reste dans le coin, j'aurai sûrement encore besoin de toi.
